<lb n="0779a25" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說盂蘭盆經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0779a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0779a27" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0779005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西〕－【宋】</note><app n="0779005"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>晉<note n="0779006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779006"><lem wit="【大】">月氏三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0779a28" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT16p0779a2801">聞如是：</p><p id="pT16p0779a2804" place="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。大
<lb n="0779a29" ed="T"/>目<note n="0779007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乾＝犍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾＝犍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779007"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">犍</rdg></app>連始得六通，欲度父母，報乳哺之恩。即
<pb n="0779b" ed="T" id="T16.0685.0779b"/>
<lb n="0779b01" ed="T"/>以道眼觀視世間，見其亡母生餓鬼中，不見
<lb n="0779b02" ed="T"/>飲食，皮骨連<note n="0779008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">立＝柱【宮】</note><app n="0779008"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">柱</rdg></app>。目連悲哀，<note n="0779009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（以）【三】</note><note n="0779009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＋（以）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779009"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">即以</rdg></app>&CB00425;盛飯，往餉
<lb n="0779b03" ed="T"/>其母。母得&CB00425;飯，便以左手障<note n="0779010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝&CB00425;【三】</note><note n="0779010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝&CB00425;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779010"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00425;</rdg></app>，右手摶<note n="0779011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779011"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0779b04" ed="T"/>食未入口，化成火炭，遂不得食。目連大叫，悲
<lb n="0779b05" ed="T"/>號<note n="0779012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啼＝涕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">啼＝涕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779012"><lem wit="【大】">啼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">涕</rdg></app>泣，馳還白佛，具陳如此。</p>
<lb n="0779b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779b0601">佛言：「汝母罪根深結，非汝一人力所奈何！汝
<lb n="0779b07" ed="T"/>雖孝順，聲動天地，天神、地<note n="0779013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝祈【宋】，祇【元】【明】</note><note n="0779013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神＝祈【宋】，＝祇【元】【明】</note><app n="0779013"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">祈</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">祇</rdg></app>、邪魔、外道、道
<lb n="0779b08" ed="T"/>士、四天王神亦不能奈何！當須十方眾僧威
<lb n="0779b09" ed="T"/>神之力乃得解脫。
<lb n="0779b10" ed="T"/>吾今當<note n="0779014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為汝〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為汝〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779014"><lem wit="【大】">為汝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>說救濟之法，令一切難皆離憂
<lb n="0779b11" ed="T"/>苦，<note n="0779015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔罪障消除〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔罪障消除〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779015"><lem wit="【大】">罪障消除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0779b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779b1201">佛告目<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K11n0277_p0621a18">連</lem><rdg wit="【大】">蓮</rdg></app>：「十方眾僧<note n="0779016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779016"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>七月十五日僧自恣
<lb n="0779b13" ed="T"/>時，當為七世父母及現在父母厄難中者，具
<lb n="0779b14" ed="T"/>飯、百味五果、汲灌盆器、香油<note n="0779017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">錠&CB02536;＝挻燭【宋】，鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0779017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錠&CB02536;＝挻燭【宋】，＝鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779017"><lem wit="【大】">錠&CB02536;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">挻燭</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">鋋燭</rdg></app>、床敷臥具、
<lb n="0779b15" ed="T"/>盡世甘美以著盆中，供養十方大德眾僧。當
<lb n="0779b16" ed="T"/>此之日，一切聖眾或在山間禪定、<note n="0779018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或〕－【宮】</note><app n="0779018"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>得四道
<lb n="0779b17" ed="T"/>果、<note n="0779019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（在）【元】【明】</note><app n="0779019"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">或在</rdg></app>樹下經行；或六通自在、教化聲聞、緣
<lb n="0779b18" ed="T"/>覺；或十地菩薩大人、權現比丘，在大眾中；皆
<lb n="0779b19" ed="T"/>同一心，受&CB00425;和羅飯。具清淨戒聖眾之道，其
<lb n="0779b20" ed="T"/>德汪洋，其有供養此等自恣僧者，現<note n="0779020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝世【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝世【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779020"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世</rdg></app>父
<lb n="0779b21" ed="T"/>母、<note n="0779021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0779021"><lem wit="【大】">七世父母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>、<note n="0779022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六種親屬＝六親眷屬【三】</note><note n="0779022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六種親屬＝六親眷屬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779022"><lem wit="【大】">六種親屬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">六親眷屬</rdg></app>得出三途之苦，應
<lb n="0779b22" ed="T"/>時解脫，衣食自然。若<note n="0779023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復有人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復有人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779023"><lem wit="【大】">復有人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>父母現在者，福
<lb n="0779b23" ed="T"/>樂百年；若<note n="0779024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已亡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔已亡〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779024"><lem wit="【大】">已亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>七世父母，生天，自在化生，入
<lb n="0779b24" ed="T"/>天華光，<note n="0779025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔受無量快樂〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔受無量快樂〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779025"><lem wit="【大】">受無量快樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。」時佛&CB00330;十方眾僧，皆
<lb n="0779b25" ed="T"/><note n="0779026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔先〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0779026"><lem wit="【大】">先</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>為施主<note n="0779027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔家〕－【宮】</note><app n="0779027"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00057;願<note n="0779028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（願）＋七【三】</note><note n="0779028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（願）＋七【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779028"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">願七</rdg></app>世父母行禪定意，然
<lb n="0779b26" ed="T"/>後受食。初受<note n="0779029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盆＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盆＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779029"><lem wit="【大】">盆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>時，先安在佛<note n="0779030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塔＝前塔寺中佛【三】</note><note n="0779030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塔＝前塔寺中佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779030"><lem wit="【大】">塔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前塔寺中佛</rdg></app>前，眾僧&CB00057;
<lb n="0779b27" ed="T"/>願竟，便自受食。</p>
<lb n="0779b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779b2801"><note n="0779031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0779031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0779031"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>時目連比丘及<note n="0779032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此大會〕－【三】，此大會＝此大眾【宮】</note><note n="0779032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此大會〕－【宋】【元】【明】，此大會＝此大眾【宮】</note><app n="0779032"><lem wit="【大】">此大會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">此大眾</rdg></app>大菩薩眾皆大
<lb n="0779b29" ed="T"/>歡喜，<note n="0779033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【三】</note><note n="0779033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔而〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779033"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>目連悲啼泣聲釋然除滅。<note n="0779034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【元】</note><app n="0779034"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>時目
<pb n="0779c" ed="T" id="T16.0685.0779c"/>
<lb n="0779c01" ed="T"/>連<note n="0779035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】</note><note n="0779035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779035"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>母即於是日，得脫一劫餓鬼之苦。</p>
<lb n="0779c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779c0201"><note n="0779036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779036"><lem wit="【大】">爾時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>目連復白佛言：「弟子所生<note n="0779037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔父〕－【三】</note><note n="0779037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔父〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779037"><lem wit="【大】">父</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>母，得蒙
<lb n="0779c03" ed="T"/>三寶功德之力，眾僧威神之力故。若未來世
<lb n="0779c04" ed="T"/>一切佛弟子<note n="0779038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行孝順者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行孝順者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779038"><lem wit="【大】">行孝順者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，<note n="0779039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦應＝應亦【宋】</note><app n="0779039"><lem wit="【大】">亦應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">應亦</rdg></app>奉<note n="0779040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779040"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>盂蘭盆，
<lb n="0779c05" ed="T"/>救度現在父母，乃至七世父母，為可爾<note n="0779041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝否【三】</note><note n="0779041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝否【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779041"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">否</rdg></app>？」</p>
<lb n="0779c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779c0601">佛言：「大善快問！我正欲說，汝今復問。善男
<lb n="0779c07" ed="T"/>子！若<note n="0779042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【明】</note><app n="0779042"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘比丘尼、國王太子、<note n="0779043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王子〕－【三】</note><note n="0779043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779043"><lem wit="【大】">王子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>大臣
<lb n="0779c08" ed="T"/>宰相、三公百官、萬民庶人行<note n="0779044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孝慈＝慈孝【三】</note><note n="0779044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孝慈＝慈孝【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779044"><lem wit="【大】">孝慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">慈孝</rdg></app>者，皆<note n="0779045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（先）【三】</note><note n="0779045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（先）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779045"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">應先</rdg></app>
<lb n="0779c09" ed="T"/>為所生現在父母、過去七世父母，於七月十
<lb n="0779c10" ed="T"/>五日——佛歡喜日、僧自恣日——以百味<note n="0779046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【元】</note><app n="0779046"><lem wit="【大】">飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">飯</rdg></app>食安
<lb n="0779c11" ed="T"/>盂蘭盆中，施十方自恣僧。<note n="0779047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乞〕－【三】</note><note n="0779047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔乞〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779047"><lem wit="【大】">乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>願<note n="0779048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779048"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>使現在
<lb n="0779c12" ed="T"/>父母壽命百年、無病，無一切苦惱之患，乃至
<lb n="0779c13" ed="T"/>七世父母離餓鬼苦，<note n="0779049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔得〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779049"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>生<note n="0779050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【三】</note><note n="0779050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天人＝人天【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779050"><lem wit="【大】">天人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">人天</rdg></app>中，<note n="0779051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝富【元】</note><app n="0779051"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">富</rdg></app>樂無
<lb n="0779c14" ed="T"/>極。」</p>
<lb n="0779c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779c1501"><note n="0779052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛告…人〕九字－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛告…人〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779052" word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">佛告諸善男子、善女人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>：「是佛弟子修孝順者，
<lb n="0779c16" ed="T"/>應念念中常憶父母，<note n="0779053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔供養〕－【三】</note><note n="0779053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔供養〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779053"><lem wit="【大】">供養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>乃至七世父母。年
<lb n="0779c17" ed="T"/>年七月十五日，<note n="0779054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】</note><note n="0779054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779054"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當</rdg></app>以孝<note n="0779055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔順〕－【三】</note><note n="0779055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔順〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779055"><lem wit="【大】">順</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>慈憶所生父母，
<lb n="0779c18" ed="T"/><note n="0779056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乃至七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0779056"><lem wit="【大】">乃至七世父母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>，為作盂蘭盆，施佛及僧，以報
<lb n="0779c19" ed="T"/>父母長養、慈愛之恩。若一切佛弟子應當奉
<lb n="0779c20" ed="T"/>持是法。」</p>
<lb n="0779c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0779c2101"><app type="＊" source="0779031"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>時目連比丘、四輩弟子，<note n="0779057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞佛所說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔聞佛所說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779057"><lem wit="【大】">聞佛所說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，歡喜
<lb n="0779c22" ed="T"/>奉行。</p></div1>
